The Scandalous Suit.  Use it to get your way.  All the time.  

*Best worn by the women, you are warned*

A Dueling Suit of Expertise is quite like it's lesser suit cousin, only with a much greater enchantment placed on it's flexibility.  Owners have sworn that the armor can actually move itself to avoid incoming attack.  These types of armors typically come in different color schemes, to match the personalities of the buyer.  This suit is orange.

An entrancing creature with a plump, shapely body. With a playful gesture, she beckons visitors closer...

Value.value: Come to me, my darling, and I will tell you a secret.
If it is power you desire, I have a task for you to prove your worth to me.
Go out into your realm. Seek the innocent.
Bring me a heart, and take a bite from it. Show me that you have the ferocity and will to lay claim to the power you seek.
Bring such a treat back to me, the Heart of an Innocent, and we shall feast together and writhe in the pleasure of power unleashed.

*A wicked grin spreads across her blood-red lips.* You have done it. Give me that from which you have tasted and take your gift. *She leans in close and offers a writhing orb of black filth.* Consume this and enjoy your new power.
There are many innocents on the Prime. Merely take the heart from one and bring it back here. Eat half of it and give it to me.
*the succubus looks at you coldly* Begone. I have no more use of you.

value.0: Please step inside and make yourself...comfortable.  We hope to provide intimate services in the very near future.  In the meantime, take a break from hectic adventuring life and indulge yourself...
